  "comment": "$$tg\\alpha =\\frac{\\sin\\alpha }{\\cos\\alpha },\\\\ где~\\cos\\alpha=\\pm\\sqrt{1-\\sin^2\\alpha}=\\pm\\sqrt{1-\\frac{26}{26^2}}=\\pm\\sqrt{1-\\frac{1}{26}}=\\pm\\sqrt{\\frac{25}{26}}\\\\ \\alpha\\in 1-ой~четверти\\Rightarrow\\cos\\alpha>0\\Rightarrow\\cos\\alpha=\\frac{\\sqrt{25}}{\\sqrt{26}}=\\frac{5}{\\sqrt{26}}\\Rightarrow\\\\ \\Rightarrow tg\\alpha=\\frac{\\sqrt{26}}{26}:\\frac{5}{\\sqrt{26}}=\\frac{\\sqrt{26}}{26}\\cdot \\frac{\\sqrt{26}}{5}=\\frac{1}{5}=0,2$$\nОтвет: 0,2",
